title: Water-T and the Rise of the Numbericons
description: His exile is over. Ice-T returns to his home on Alphabetrium to once again become Water-T just as the Numbericons begin their attack.
altHero: in a grand hall, a letter T made of water with a face holds up two guns
alt1: a fantasy world with buildings and people shaped like letters
alt2: letters J, F, and Q point staffs that create a ball of light above an ice person (Ice-T)
alt3: Water-T holds Magma-Q as he is dying
alt4: Water-T busts through a door shooting at the Numbericons, snake-like numbers
